'''愛爾蘭問題'''（Irish Question），1800年至1920年間困擾[[大英帝國|大英帝國]]的[[國族問題|國族問題]]，最通行定義出自1844年英國議員[[本傑明·迪斯雷利|本傑明·迪斯雷利]]（後來的[[英國首相|英國首相]]）：「A dense population, in extreme distress, inhabit an island where there is an Established Church, which is not their Church, and a territorial aristocracy the richest of whom live in foreign capitals. Thus you have a starving population, an absentee aristocracy, and an alien Church; and in addition the weakest executive in the world. That is the Irish Question.」（中譯：[前略]...饥饿的人口、在外贵族、外国教会，加上世上最弱的执行政府，這就是愛爾蘭問題）。<ref>{{cite journal|title=《简·爱》里的“爱尔兰问题”|journal=《外国文学评论》|date=2012|issue=2|last=王苹|first=|url=|}} 全文公開於：{{cite news|title=《简·爱》里的“爱尔兰问题”|newspaper=凤凰资讯|date=2018-06-05|last=|first=|url=http://inews.ifeng.com/yidian/59025857/news.shtml|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212154411/http://inews.ifeng.com/yidian/59025857/news.shtml|archivedate=2020-12-12|accessdate=2020-12-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>

